flowchart TD
    A["src/backend/routers/agent.py::runtime_agent_run\nTrigger: POST /api/agents/run\nData: RuntimeAgentRunRequest\nWhy: entrypoint for runtime execution"] --> B["src/backend/services/agent_service.py::run_runtime_agent\nTrigger: router call\nData: payload + DB session\nWhy: preserve API contract while delegating runtime orchestration"]

    B --> C["src/backend/agents/langgraph_agent.py::LangGraphAgentScaffold.run\nTrigger: service invokes runtime scaffold\nData: payload.query + optional persistence fields\nWhy: execute decomposition -> tool selection -> delegated subquery path"]

    C --> D["src/backend/agents/langgraph_agent.py::build_subquery_execution_tool\nTrigger: run() binds DB-backed tool\nData: SQLAlchemy Session\nWhy: expose retrieval+validation as callable subagent tool"]

    C --> E["src/backend/agents/langgraph_agent.py::get_subagents\nTrigger: run() requests runtime subagent defs\nData: required DeepAgent keys (name, description, system_prompt, tools)\nWhy: provide specialized subquery-executor subagent"]

    D --> E

    C --> F["Delegation loop in LangGraphAgentScaffold.run\nTrigger: each SubQueryToolAssignment\nData: (sub_query, tool)\nWhy: emulate DeepAgent task path per subquery"]

    F --> G["Delegated tool callable (_tool)\nsrc/backend/agents/langgraph_agent.py::build_subquery_execution_tool.<locals>._tool\nData out: retrieval_result + validation_result + single summary\nWhy: return concise delegated result while retaining full downstream artifacts"]

    G --> H["src/backend/services/retrieval_service.py::execute_subquery_retrieval\nTrigger: delegated tool\nData: SubQueryToolAssignment\nWhy: retrieve evidence from assigned tool"]

    G --> I["src/backend/services/validation_service.py::validate_retrieval_result\nTrigger: delegated tool after retrieval\nData: SubQueryRetrievalResult\nWhy: enforce sufficiency loop before synthesis"]

    G --> J["src/backend/agents/langgraph_agent.py::_build_delegated_subquery_summary\nTrigger: delegated tool after validation\nData: retrieval + validation outputs\nWhy: emit one concise summary per delegated subquery"]

    F --> K["graph_state.timeline\nEvents: subagent.delegation started/completed + existing retrieval/validation steps\nWhy: make delegation observable to smoke tests and UI consumers"]

    F --> L["graph_state.graph.execution\nFields: subagents[], delegations[]\nWhy: expose task-path delegation metadata without changing top-level response schema"]

    N1["Decision: keep top-level retrieval_results/validation_results contract unchanged.\nTradeoff: duplicate representation (summary + full artifacts) but avoids frontend/API breakage."] --- L
    N2["Decision: task-path delegation is metadata-backed in scaffold mode (deterministic callable).\nTradeoff: true deepagents runtime task invocation can replace internals later with same metadata contract."] --- F
